text: World in My Corner is a 1956 American drama movie directed by Jesse Hibbs and starring Audie Murphy, Barbara Rush, Jeff Morrow, John McIntire, Tommy Rall, Howard St. John, Art Aragon, Jimmy Lennon. It was distributed by Universal Pictures. ==Other websites== * * Category:1956 drama movies Category:American drama movies Category:Universal Pictures movies Category:Movies directed by Jesse Hibbs
title: World in My Corner
